snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | What mask are you?
snippet.description:
Wearing a mask is sometimes amusing. But for some it is more like a comforter. Something that keeps you sane and balanced. But even someone calm can be startled, and someone spooked might go berserk and bring you to slaughter.
